Class RedBlackTree

java.lang.Object
  |

        +--xxl.binarySearchTrees.RedBlackTree
public class RedBlackTree
extends BinarySearchTree

A binary tree that is equivalent to a 2-3-tree. The RedBlackTree provides insertion and exactmatch search in O(log(n)) time.

For a detailed discussion see "Introduction to Algorithms", MIT Electrical Engineering and Computer Science, by Thomas H. Cormen, Charles E. Leiserson, Ronald L. Rivest.
